name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
(
    EXISTS(SELECT * FROM IBZUSER_ROLE t11
                             LEFT JOIN IBZROLE t21 ON t11.SYS_ROLEID = t21.SYS_ROLEID
           WHERE
               t1.USERID = t11.USERID  AND (<#assign _value=srfwebcontext('roletag','{"ignoreempty":true,"defname":"ROLETAG","dename":"SYS_USER_ROLE"}')><#if _value?length gt 0>t21.ROLETAG =  ${_value}<#else>1=1</#if> ) )
    OR
    EXISTS(SELECT * FROM sys_role_member t11
               LEFT JOIN IBZROLE t21 ON t11.ROLE_ID = t21.SYS_ROLEID
               WHERE
               t1.USERID = t11.USERID  AND (<#assign _value=srfwebcontext('roletag','{"ignoreempty":true,"defname":"ROLETAG","dename":"SYS_USER_ROLE"}')><#if _value?length gt 0>t21.ROLETAG =  ${_value}<#else>1=1</#if> ) )
)
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: ( t1.STATE <> '0'  AND  ( #{ctx.webcontext.excuserid} IS NULL OR  t1.USERID <> #{ctx.webcontext.excuserid}   ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
    t1.ADDR,
    t1.AVATAR,
    t1.BCODE,
    t1.BIRTHDAY,
    t1.CERTCODE,
    t1.CREATEDATE,
    t1.DDUNIONID,
    t1.DDUSERID,
    t1.DOMAINS,
    t1.EMAIL,
    t1.ENABLE,
    t1.FONTSIZE,
    t1.FROMOPENUSERTAG,
    t1.IPADDR,
    t1.LANG,
    t1.LOGINNAME,
    t1.MDEPTCODE,
    t1.MDEPTID,
    t1.MDEPTNAME,
    t1.MEMO,
    t1.MSGTYPE,
    t1.NICKNAME,
    t1.ORGCODE,
    t1.ORGID,
    t1.ORGNAME,
    t1.PASSWORD,
    t1.PERSONNAME,
    t1.PHONE,
    t1.POSTCODE,
    t1.POSTID,
    t1.POSTNAME,
    t1.RESERVER,
    t1.RESERVER10,
    t1.RESERVER11,
    t1.RESERVER12,
    t1.RESERVER13,
    t1.RESERVER14,
    t1.RESERVER15,
    t1.RESERVER16,
    t1.RESERVER17,
    t1.RESERVER18,
    t1.RESERVER19,
    t1.RESERVER2,
    t1.RESERVER20,
    t1.RESERVER3,
    t1.RESERVER4,
    t1.RESERVER5,
    t1.RESERVER6,
    t1.RESERVER7,
    t1.RESERVER8,
    t1.RESERVER9,
    t1.SEX,
    t1.SHOWORDER,
    t1.STATE,
    t1.SUPERUSER,
    t1.THEME,
    t1.UAAUSERID,
    t1.UPDATEDATE,
    t1.USERCODE,
    t1.USERICON,
    t1.USERID,
    t1.USERNAME,
    t1.WXWORKUNIONID,
    t1.WXWORKUSERID,
    t1.SRFDCID
FROM (SELECT
          t1.POSTAL_ADDRESS as ADDR,
          t1.AVATAR,
          d.BUSINESS_CATEGORY as BCODE,
          null as BIRTHDAY,
          t1.IDENTIFICATION_NUMBER as CERTCODE,
          t1.CREATE_TIME as CREATEDATE,
          t1.IDENTIFICATION_NUMBER as DDUNIONID,
          t1.EMPLOYEE_NUMBER as DDUSERID,
          t1.DC as DOMAINS,
          t1.MAIL as EMAIL,
          t1.ENABLED as ENABLE,
          null as FONTSIZE,
          t1.IDENTIFICATION_NUMBER as FROMOPENUSERTAG,
          t1.POSTAL_ADDRESS as IPADDR,
          null as LANG,
          t1.UID as LOGINNAME,
          d.DEPARTMENT_NUMBER as MDEPTCODE,
          t1.MDEPARTMENT_ID as MDEPTID,
          d.DEPARTMENT_NAME as MDEPTNAME,
          t1.DESCRIPTION as MEMO,
          null as MSGTYPE,
          t1.DISPLAY_NAME as NICKNAME,
          o.ORGANIZATION_NUMBER as ORGCODE,
          t1.ORGANIZATION_ID as ORGID,
          o.ORGANIZATION_NAME as ORGNAME,
          t1.USER_PASSWORD as PASSWORD,
          t1.DISPLAY_NAME as PERSONNAME,
          t1.MOBILE as PHONE,
          null as POSTCODE,
          null as POSTID,
          null as POSTNAME,
          null as RESERVER,
          null as RESERVER10,
          null as RESERVER11,
          null as RESERVER12,
          null as RESERVER13,
          null as RESERVER14,
          null as RESERVER15,
          null as RESERVER16,
          null as RESERVER17,
          null as RESERVER18,
          null as RESERVER19,
          null as RESERVER2,
          null as RESERVER20,
          null as RESERVER3,
          null as RESERVER4,
          null as RESERVER5,
          null as RESERVER6,
          null as RESERVER7,
          null as RESERVER8,
          null as RESERVER9,
          null as SEX,
          8888 as SHOWORDER,
          t1.STATUS as STATE,
          null as SUPERUSER,
          null as THEME,
          t1.ID as UAAUSERID,
          t1.UPDATE_TIME as UPDATEDATE,
          t1.EMPLOYEE_NUMBER as USERCODE,
          null as USERICON,
          t1.ID as USERID,
          t1.UID as  USERNAME,
          t1.TELEPHONE_NUMBER as WXWORKUNIONID,
          t1.EMPLOYEE_NUMBER as WXWORKUSERID,
          o.DC as SRFDCID
      FROM sys_person t1 left join sys_organization o on t1.ORGANIZATION_ID=o.ID
                         left join sys_department d on t1.MDEPARTMENT_ID = d.ID
     ) t1
